sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend as React Frontend
    participant Backend as Flask Backend
    participant Groq as Groq LLM

    User->>Frontend: Types natural language query
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/query {query}

    Note over Backend: Superlative check first (tallest/cheapest etc.)<br/>then Groq, then regex fallback

    Backend->>Groq: Chat completion request with few-shot prompt
    alt Groq returns valid filter JSON
        Groq-->>Backend: filters array
        Backend->>Backend: Apply filters to buildings dataset
        Backend-->>Frontend: matched_ids + filters + method "llm"
        Frontend->>Frontend: Highlight matched buildings in Flames red
        Frontend->>Frontend: Update status badge and method badge
    else Groq fails or returns unparseable response
        Groq-->>Backend: Error or invalid JSON
        Backend->>Backend: Regex fallback or return no-match
        Backend-->>Frontend: matched_ids + method "fallback" or error
    end
